### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/health

### Agent test (ישיר)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/agent/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "web",
  "from_user": "972501234567",
  "text": "שלום, אשמח לפרטים"
}

### WhatsApp webhook (סימולציה)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json
X-Signature: test

{
  "entry": [
    {"changes":[
      {"value":{
        "messages":[{"from":"972501234567","text":{"body":"מה המחיר?"}}]
      }}]
    }
  ]
}
